			<div class="h-2 ml-4 bg-gradient-to-r grow my-auto from-red via-yellow to-blue rounded-full"></div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="motion-preset-blur-right motion-delay-300">
			<p class="text-text whitespace-pre-line lg:w-3/4"> i have a lot of projects... and a lot of them are abandoned. ¯\_(ツ)_/¯ here's all the ones i can remember...

			</p>

			<p class="text-text whitespace-pre-line w-3/4">I've worked on quite a lot of projects, and I've abandoned most of them. ¯\_(ツ)_/¯
                Here are a few of my favourites:</p>
    
                <Project title="Personal website" link="https://example.com" source="Hex-4/website" badge="shipped">
                    You're here right now! After many, many iterations, (hopefully) this is the last. Made with my usual stack (Astro, Tailwind + Catppuccin, Cloudflare Pages) but this time I used this shiny new library called <a class="underline underline-offset-4   transition-all hover:font-extrabold hover:underline-offset-8 decoration-wavy hover:text-yellow" href="https://rombo.co/tailwind">tailwindcss-motion</a> for these fancy animations.
                </Project>
                <Project title="Galaxium//ONE" link="https://the-dimaverse.itch.io/galaxiumone" badge="frozen">
                    My first publicly released game, made with the Lazy Devs shump tutorial in PICO-8. Also has two content updates!
                </Project>
                <Project title="Big Slime, Lil' Slime" link="https://the-dimaverse.itch.io/galaxiumone" source="Hex-4/gmtk-2024" badge="frozen">
                    I'm really proud of this one. Made in 48 hours for the GMTK Game Jam 2024, placing #3617 out of over 7000 games. All art and code is original, with some AMAZING music by Kevin MacLeod. Open it in Godot to take a peek inside!
                </Project>
                <Project title="potatoe simlater." link="https://the-dimaverse.itch.io/potatoe" badge="frozen">
                    I have no idea why I made this.
                </Project>
                <Project title="Hexapad" link="https://cad.onshape.com/documents/2133e09e1f245de59bbe7858/w/b4533889f6300572d81eb032/e/b0c575e6e2f32d509dfa7b54" source="Hex-4/hexapad" badge="shipped">
